body:
Swiss Garden Resort Residences – Rare 3-Storey Beachfront Townhouse

The residence is a stunning, newly refurbished 3-storey beachfront townhouse nestled right along the scenic Balok Beach coastline. Located within the prestigious Swiss Garden Resort Residences, this rare townhouse unit (only 12 in the entire development!) offers a comfortable and convenient lifestyle for those seeking a peaceful seaside home.

Whether you’re looking for a short-term or a long-term stay, this move-in-ready property is perfect for expats, professionals, or families who appreciate comfort, convenience, and the peaceful environment.

Key Highlights

● Rare Townhouse Unit (3-Sorey) – Just 12 units in the entire development
● Newly Refurbished & Highly Well-Kept – New and comfortable living space, with repainted walls, rebuilt staircase, all brand-new air conditioners & beddings
● Fully Equipped & Move-In Ready – Save time & money on setup
● Prime Beachfront Location - Direct access to the beautiful Balok Beach. Jog at beach in the morning & evening
● Resort-Style Amenities - Experience the best of both nature & modern living

Spacious Layout

● Popular Among Senior Expats & Professionals

● Washing Machine, Dryer, Drying Rack
● High-Quality Sofas, Curtains, and Lighting
● All Brand New & Comfortable Beds with Brand New Clean Linens
● Water Heaters in All Bathroom
● Wardrobes & Ample Storage
● High Speed Wi-Fi – Work or stream seamlessly
● Smart TV with Netflix & Karaoke System – For family fun & entertainment

Prime and Strategic Location

● Super Convenient Location with Supermarkets Nearby – 5 minutes drive to TMG Mart Batu Hitam for fresh groceries and daily essentials
● Close to Kuantan Town Centre – 20 minutes drive to town centre, quick access to shopping malls, hospitals, and city amenities
● Safe and Peaceful Environment – 24-hour guarded and gated residence
● Convenience Stores and Mini Marts within the Area – All your everyday needs just steps away
● Strategically Located for Professionals Working in Gebeng Industrial Zone – A top choice among expats and long-term residents

Top Choice Stay in Kuantan

✔️ Rare seafront townhouse – just 12 units in the entire development
✔️ Enjoy resort-style facilities daily without the hotel crowd
✔️ Wake up to ocean views & walk to the beach in seconds

Venice Hill refers to a freehold condominium located at Batu 9 Cheras in Cheras South. The developer of this property is Li-Foong Group while its design is courtesy of an architect company based in Malaysia which is known as Ehrlich Layton International Architecture. From this condominium, you’ll be able to enjoy the beautiful views of the surrounding lush greeneries as well as the KLCC. The residential property enjoys huge demand, especially from the expatriates in the locality, all its units having been sold in a six-month time following its launching. Completed in 2000, this vibrant condo is made up of 12 condominium blocks which are 17 to 30 storey high. The built-up areas of the units in this property range from 1,200 square feet to 1,600 square feet. The units come in five different layouts. The development also contains penthouses in its roof level. The property hosts an array of facilities including a sauna, gym, swimming pool, mini-market, eatery, reading room, covered car park, jogging path, playground for kids as well as 24-hour security. The nearby amenities include shopping malls, convenient stores, restaurants, religious places, pharmacies, clinics, hospitals, banks schools, colleges and universities.

Venice Hill is a good home, either for self-occupancy or as an investment for rental returns. The living experience plus the atmosphere here are fantastic. People who reside here have the privilege of enjoying the cool waft from the nearby rainforest, right from the comfort of their homes. In fact, air conditioners aren’t part of the necessities of the residents because nature has already sorted them out. Besides, the residents whose units face the city centre have an additional advantage of having panoramic views of the surrounding skyline lush greeneries and the city centre of Kuala Lumpur. The property mostly attracts foreigners who want a modern condo lifestyle since it is located near the city centre as well as the wide range of facilities that it provides for convenient living. The foreign occupants don’t hassle to quench their thirst for education since there are is an international college and an international school in the vicinity of the property. Furthermore, the units in this condominium are sold at very competitive prices. However, the value of the property keeps on appreciating at a rapid rate, given its prime location which is easily accessible through various major routes.

Venice Hill can be easily accessed from various major destinations in Selangor such as townships and commercial areas through Jalan Hulu Langat as well as Cheras-Kajang highway. Its occupants enjoy the convenience of accessing various public amenities which are located in the neighborhood of the property. For easy access to education, the vicinity hosts various education institutions such as Cempaka International School, SJKC Taman Connaught, SK Taman Puteri, SJK Taman Bukit Teratai, Masterskill University College of Health Sciences, SJK Taman Segar, as well as SMK Taman Seraya. Shopping is an effortless affair to the residents of the condo, given that various shops lots and shopping malls like Cheras Sentral Mall and Leisure Mall are just stone throw’s distance away. The residents can only starve at their free will as they only require to walk briefly to get various dishes from the neighboring fast food joints and restaurants like Restoran Gaia Bistro, Restoran Heng Ong Huat D'Pallet Place and Nana Western Seafood. Other nearby conveniences include various worship places, petrol stations, police stations, pharmacies, banks.

Spacious Living & Dining
Step into an open‑plan living area bathed in natural light from balcony entrance door. Plush sofas, a stylish coffee table that set the stage for relaxed evenings or lively gatherings, while the adjacent dining zone, complete with a sleek table for six, makes entertaining effortless.

Three Serene Bedrooms

Bedroom 2 & 3: Ideal for guests and children, these rooms each include a queen‑size bed, a bunk bed and built‑in wardrobes.

Two Modern Bathrooms

Expansive Balcony

Two Dedicated Car Parks

Tiara Imperio @ Bangi Accessibility and Amenities
Public transportation that is nearby include KTM UKM which is about a 15 minutes’ walk / 2 minutes’ drive away (1.2km), the UKM Komuter bus stand at 1.38km away as well as the Kajang Bus Terminal whichi is a little further away at 2.53km. Schools nearby include SMK Jalan Tiga which is about 2.33km away and SJK (T) Bangi which is about 2.6km away. Tertiary education institutions that are in the area include the German Malaysian Institute which is a mere 0.23km away and University Kebangsaan Malaysia (UKM) which is 2.37km away. Tiara Imperio @ Bangi is also just a short drive to the Scenic and Danau Golf Course. Tiara Imperio @ Bangi is accessible via main roads and major expressways such as Jalan Bangi Lama, the North South expressway as well as the Kajang Seremban Highway and is only a 30 minute drive to Kuala Lumpur city center. The IOI Mall Putrajaya is about 25 minutes away. There are plenty of eateries and shops close by as well. If medical assistance is ever needed, one can head over to the government run Klinik Kesihatan Bandar Baru Bangi which is only 2.98km away.

Tiara Imperio @ Bangi offers its residents full facilities. There is a 40 meter swimming pool to cool off in during a hot day, a multi-purpose hall, a barbeque area to cook up a delicious meal and a pool side gym room for residents to keep fit and healthy. For residents who prefer something quieter, there is the activity and reading room. Families with children can head over to the kids’ playground, and wading pool. The Tiara Convention Hall is available for residents to host events and functions. There is also a kindergarten, retail shops, sundry shops and a cafeteria for residents’ convenience. Tiara Imperio @ Bangi is a gated and guarded property with an 8 tier security system including CCTV, smart card access system and 24 hour security to ensure residents’ safety.

Enjoy the best of both worlds in this beautifully presented 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom condominium—fully furnished and featuring a partial seaview that adds a refreshing coastal touch to your daily living. Perfectly suited for families, professionals, or students, this home combines practicality with peaceful charm in a sought-after location.

Wake up to calming sea breezes and unwind in the evenings with a view of the horizon —ideal for sipping coffee, working remotely, or enjoying a quiet sunset moment.

Bedroom 2 & 3: Great for guests, kids, or a home office—each fully furnished and move-in ready.

Arena Green@ Bukit Jalil is the right place for you, if living inside a lustful greenery coupled with royal amenities in a developing area is in your mind. It is a flawless work of one of the pioneer property developer of Malaysia, Berjaya Land Berhad thus bears the promise of quality interior as well as outer finishing.

From this place, travelling to any part of the city will not be an issue as some major KTM stations such as Bandar Tasik Selatan, Serdang, Pantai Dalam, Petaling are present within 3 km of radius. For giving proper education to your children, there are numerous education institutes such as Smk Bukit Jalil, Institut Sukan Negara, Tpm Academy and Asia Pacific University of Technology and Innovation. Getting immediate medical attention is also very easy due to the presence of followings; Klinik Mediviron, Klinik Elamedic, Dentiste’Clinic and Yan Specialist Women Clinic. You can also fetch groceries for youe daily needs from major shopping destinations such as 7-Eleven, Carrefour, Endah Parade and KK Supermart etc.

Arena Green is marking its presence near Bukit Jalil therefore; it is hardly a case that you will feel bored as there are plenty of attractive places nearby to roam around. Th Parliament house is present few kilometres away and also is the Roller Sports World to have a good time with your mate. Those who are art lovers they can make their presence at Islamic Arts Museum present near to Jalan Lembah. Now, if you love to get massage do hit places like Reborn Foot Reflexology and Ozmosis Health & Day spa.

Most of the condos in Bukit Jalil have parking issues but same is not the case over here as you will get a wide covered parking area where your costly sport car can even glide in very easily. To recreate some unforgettable moments with the dearer ones, there is a club house present exclusively for the insiders of Arena Green and also, a Mini Market is situated downstairs to take care of the daily needs of the residents. The list of additional amenities includes the elements like a saloon, a cafeteria and a 24-hour convenient store; this is quite impossible to get at any other nearby condo under such budget price range. Fitness freaks can best utilise their time by running around a Jogging Track or by playing some activities inside a wide Playground present backside.

body:
🌟 Experience the perfect blend of comfort, convenience, and modern living in this medium-level unit at the highly sought-after Kinrara Ria Apartment, located in Taman Kinrara Seksyen 4, Puchong. Designed for young professionals, especially office staff, this unit is your sanctuary in the heart of a thriving community.

🏡 Property Features
- Spacious 852 sqft Apartment
- 3 Bedrooms, 2 Bathrooms for optimal privacy and functionality
- 1 Dedicated Parking Lot for your convenience
- Gated & Guarded Community with 24-hour security for peace of mind
- Fully Renovated with RM85K worth of premium upgrades- Built-in Kitchen Cabinet for easy cooking
- Built-in Iron Clothes Drying Rack for efficiency
- Installed Ventilation Fan to keep the air fresh
- Sleek Tiles Table-Top for extra style and functionality

- Internet Fiber Ready for seamless connectivity
- Move-In Ready with modern finishes and ample natural light
- Fun Playground to unwind and relax


📍 Convenient Location
Nestled in a strategic area, this property offers easy access to a host of amenities and recreational options:
Shopping: IOI Mall Puchong, Tesco Extra Puchong, Giant Hypermarket, and The Store for all your retail needs.
Education: Nearby SJK(C) Yak Chee, SMK Seksyen 3 Kinrara, and Taylor's Lakeside University for those pursuing education.
Healthcare: Proximity to KPMC Puchong Specialist Centre and Columbia Asia Hospital - Puchong for quality medical care.
Recreation: Enjoy leisure activities at Kinrara Golf Club, Taman Rekreasi Bukit Jalil, and Ayer Hitam Forest Reserve.

🚗 Unparalleled Accessibility
This location boasts excellent connectivity with:
- Major Highways: LDP, KESAS, Bukit Jalil Highway, and MEX, making commuting a breeze
- Public Transport: Sri Petaling LRT Station, Taman Kinrara LRT Station, and ample bus services

Why wait? This Kinrara Ria Apartment unit offers a perfect living solution tailored for office staff looking for convenience, security, and a modern lifestyle. Contact us today to arrange a viewing and seize this opportunity!

body:
Swiss Garden Resort Residences – Rare 3-Storey Beachfront Townhouse

The residence is a stunning, newly refurbished 3-storey beachfront townhouse nestled right along the scenic Balok Beach coastline. Located within the prestigious Swiss Garden Resort Residences, this rare townhouse unit (only 12 in the entire development!) offers a comfortable and convenient lifestyle for those seeking a peaceful seaside home.

Whether you’re looking for a short-term or a long-term stay, this move-in-ready property is perfect for expats, professionals, or families who appreciate comfort, convenience, and the peaceful environment.

Key Highlights

● Rare Townhouse Unit (3-Sorey) – Just 12 units in the entire development
● Newly Refurbished & Highly Well-Kept – New and comfortable living space, with repainted walls, rebuilt staircase, all brand-new air conditioners & beddings
● Fully Equipped & Move-In Ready – Save time & money on setup
● Prime Beachfront Location - Direct access to the beautiful Balok Beach. Jog at beach in the morning & evening
● Resort-Style Amenities - Experience the best of both nature & modern living
● Popular Among Expats & Professionals Woking Nearby Gebeng

Spacious Layout

● 4 Bedrooms, 4.5 Bathrooms
● 2 Spacious Living Rooms, each with panoramic seaview
● Fully Equipped Kitchen & Dining Area
● Laundry Area with Washing Machine & Dryer Provided
● Private Rooftop with Breathtaking Seaview
● Large Swimming Pool Area & Waterpark
● Popular Among Senior Expats & Professionals

Fully Equipped & Move-In Ready

● Fridge, Oven, Microwave, Induction Stove, Kettle
● Dining Table with 6-8 Pax Seating
● Washing Machine, Dryer, Drying Rack
● High-Quality Sofas, Curtains, and Lighting
● All Brand New & Comfortable Beds with Brand New Clean Linens
● Water Heaters in All Bathroom
● Wardrobes & Ample Storage
● High Speed Wi-Fi – Work or stream seamlessly
● Smart TV with Netflix & Karaoke System – For family fun & entertainment

Prime and Strategic Location

● Super Convenient Location with Supermarkets Nearby – 5 minutes drive to TMG Mart Batu Hitam for fresh groceries and daily essentials
● Close to Kuantan Town Centre – 20 minutes drive to town centre, quick access to shopping malls, hospitals, and city amenities
● Safe and Peaceful Environment – 24-hour guarded and gated residence
● Convenience Stores and Mini Marts within the Area – All your everyday needs just steps away
● Strategically Located for Professionals Working in Gebeng Industrial Zone – A top choice among expats and long-term residents

Top Choice Stay in Kuantan

✔️ Rare seafront townhouse – just 12 units in the entire development
✔️ Enjoy resort-style facilities daily without the hotel crowd
✔️ Wake up to ocean views & walk to the beach in seconds
✔️ Experience the best of both nature & modern living
✔️ Move-in ready – save time & money on setup
✔️ A favourite pick for long-term expats & professionals

body:
Swiss Garden Resort Residences – Rare 3-Storey Beachfront Townhouse

The residence is a stunning, newly refurbished 3-storey beachfront townhouse nestled right along the scenic Balok Beach coastline. Located within the prestigious Swiss Garden Resort Residences, this rare townhouse unit (only 12 in the entire development!) offers a comfortable and convenient lifestyle for those seeking a peaceful seaside home.

Whether you’re looking for a short-term or a long-term stay, this move-in-ready property is perfect for expats, professionals, or families who appreciate comfort, convenience, and the peaceful environment.

Key Highlights

● Rare Townhouse Unit (3-Sorey) – Just 12 units in the entire development
● Newly Refurbished & Highly Well-Kept – New and comfortable living space, with repainted walls, rebuilt staircase, all brand-new air conditioners & beddings
● Fully Equipped & Move-In Ready – Save time & money on setup
● Prime Beachfront Location - Direct access to the beautiful Balok Beach. Jog at beach in the morning & evening
● Resort-Style Amenities - Experience the best of both nature & modern living
● Popular Among Expats & Professionals Woking Nearby Gebeng

Spacious Layout

● 4 Bedrooms, 4.5 Bathrooms
● 2 Spacious Living Rooms, each with panoramic seaview
● Fully Equipped Kitchen & Dining Area
● Laundry Area with Washing Machine & Dryer Provided
● Private Rooftop with Breathtaking Seaview
● Large Swimming Pool Area & Waterpark
● Popular Among Senior Expats & Professionals

Fully Equipped & Move-In Ready

● Fridge, Oven, Microwave, Induction Stove, Kettle
● Dining Table with 6-8 Pax Seating
● Washing Machine, Dryer, Drying Rack
● High-Quality Sofas, Curtains, and Lighting
● All Brand New & Comfortable Beds with Brand New Clean Linens
● Water Heaters in All Bathroom
● Wardrobes & Ample Storage
● High Speed Wi-Fi – Work or stream seamlessly
● Smart TV with Netflix & Karaoke System – For family fun & entertainment

Prime and Strategic Location

● Super Convenient Location with Supermarkets Nearby – 5 minutes drive to TMG Mart Batu Hitam for fresh groceries and daily essentials
● Close to Kuantan Town Centre – 20 minutes drive to town centre, quick access to shopping malls, hospitals, and city amenities
● Safe and Peaceful Environment – 24-hour guarded and gated residence
● Convenience Stores and Mini Marts within the Area – All your everyday needs just steps away
● Strategically Located for Professionals Working in Gebeng Industrial Zone – A top choice among expats and long-term residents

Top Choice Stay in Kuantan

✔️ Rare seafront townhouse – just 12 units in the entire development
✔️ Enjoy resort-style facilities daily without the hotel crowd
✔️ Wake up to ocean views & walk to the beach in seconds
✔️ Experience the best of both nature & modern living
✔️ Move-in ready – save time & money on setup
✔️ A favourite pick for long-term expats & professionals

About Sentul Village Mercury
=============================
Sentul Village is an uniquely designed residence located in Sentul, Kuala Lumpur. UOA Group is the developer of this apartment and it expected to finish in 2017. This is a 26-story freehold serviced apartment. It comprises of 462 units with developed ranges of 948 to 1,032 sq ft. There are six unique designs at Sentul Village, by which all units have 3 rooms and 2 washrooms with variation developed territories. Each unit at Sentul Village will get a picturesque perspective of Batu Caves see, KL see, greenery view or swimming pool see.

Surrounding Mercury Serviced Apartment @ Sentul Village are numerous schools, namely Sekolah Kebangsaan Batu Muda, SJK (C) Sentul Pasar, Sekolah Kebangsaan Sentul 1, Sekolah Kebangsaan Sentul 2 and SM Chong Hwa to name a few.
Mercury Serviced Apartment @ Sentul Village is strategically located and is easily accessible using the Duta-Ulu Kelang Expressway (DUKE) and Middle Ring Road 2 (MRR2) highways while the Sentul Timur LRT Station and Sentul KTM station are just 1.5km and 3km away respectively. Getting to Kuala Lumpur City Centre will require approximately 5 minutes when traffic is clear.

Well connected to major expressways and public transportations, Mercury Serviced Apartment @ Sentul Village offers exceptional convenience of city living.

Swiss Garden Resort Residences – Rare 3-Storey Beachfront Townhouse

The residence is a stunning, newly refurbished 3-storey beachfront townhouse nestled right along the scenic Balok Beach coastline. Located within the prestigious Swiss Garden Resort Residences, this rare townhouse unit (only 12 in the entire development!) offers a comfortable and convenient lifestyle for those seeking a peaceful seaside home.

Whether you’re looking for a short-term or a long-term stay, this move-in-ready property is perfect for expats, professionals, or families who appreciate comfort, convenience, and the peaceful environment.

Key Highlights

● Rare Townhouse Unit (3-Sorey) – Just 12 units in the entire development
● Newly Refurbished & Highly Well-Kept – New and comfortable living space, with repainted walls, rebuilt staircase, all brand-new air conditioners & beddings
● Fully Equipped & Move-In Ready – Save time & money on setup
● Prime Beachfront Location - Direct access to the beautiful Balok Beach. Jog at beach in the morning & evening
● Resort-Style Amenities - Experience the best of both nature & modern living

Spacious Layout

● Fridge, Oven, Microwave, Induction Stove, Kettle

● All Brand New & Comfortable Beds with Brand New Clean Linens
● Water Heaters in All Bathroom
● Wardrobes & Ample Storage
● High Speed Wi-Fi – Work or stream seamlessly
● Smart TV with Netflix & Karaoke System – For family fun & entertainment

Prime and Strategic Location

● Super Convenient Location with Supermarkets Nearby – 5 minutes drive to TMG Mart Batu Hitam for fresh groceries and daily essentials
● Close to Kuantan Town Centre – 20 minutes drive to town centre, quick access to shopping malls, hospitals, and city amenities
● Safe and Peaceful Environment – 24-hour guarded and gated residence
● Convenience Stores and Mini Marts within the Area – All your everyday needs just steps away
● Strategically Located for Professionals Working in Gebeng Industrial Zone – A top choice among expats and long-term residents

Top Choice Stay in Kuantan

✔️ Rare seafront townhouse – just 12 units in the entire development
✔️ Enjoy resort-style facilities daily without the hotel crowd
✔️ Wake up to ocean views & walk to the beach in seconds
✔️ Experience the best of both nature & modern living

* I rent this house for 3 years, nowdays moving others area. Honestly speaking i have no complaint for this SL6 taman. super good community, strict guard house control, front have big green park, easy parking 2 cars, all friendly neighbour, kids can walking to school within gate and guarded area from primary school to high school just 5 min.

* Prefer chinese family, Not Racism, cause we cooked non-halal food in kitchen. and 90% of this taman is chinese family, some traditional festival worship burning somehthing might cause uncomfortable, sure if not mind its welcome.

We have good neighborhood here ,so hope can find a responsible tenant to take over this house. Belive its the lowest price to rent a good 2sty house among this area.

Lebuhraya Damansara- Puchong (LDP) expressway, New Pantai Expressway (NPE), Federal Highway, Kesas Highway as well as through Old Klang Road and PJ Old Town. The area is also served by numerous public transportation such as buses and taxis which ply the route on a daily basis. Sri Manja Square is a convenient area to converge as it offers a host of services to offer patrons and residents alike. The area is surrounded by numerous schools such as Sekolah Jenis Kebangsaan (C ) Yuk Chyun, SMK Petaling, Sekolah Kebangsaan (1 ) Petaling Jaya, SJK (C) Chen Moh, Sekolah Kebangsaan Seri Suria, Sekolah Kebangsaan Taman Dato Harun (2) , Sekolah Rendah Sathya Sai, SJK (C ) Yak Chee Puchong, Sekolah Kebangsaan Assunta Satu, SK 2 Petaling Jaya, Sekolah Kebangsaan Petaling Jaya and Sekolah Kebangsaan Seri Mega. In addition, Giant Superstore Sri Manja is but a mere minute away on foot while other mini-market or supermarket like 99 Speed Mart, Pasar Raya Wah Fong, NTT Mini Market and TF Mini Market are not too far away. There are also banks to assist in smooth business process like Ambank, Hong Leong Bank and Maybank as well as a number of ATM machines scattered around Sri Manja Square. The nearest post office is the Pos Malaysia Taman Kinrara which is about a kilometre away. For food there is always Ayam Golek Ameen Shah, Restoran Maya Thai, Uncle Jack, Domino’s Sri Manja, KFC, Restoran Fai Wong and many others, which is too much to mention, within Sri Manja Square and its neighbouring townships. Amongst the facilities available here include over a thousand indoor parking bays as well as pedestrian walkway which is 670’ long.

Arena Green@ Bukit Jalil is the right place for you, if living inside a lustful greenery coupled with royal amenities in a developing area is in your mind. It is a flawless work of one of the pioneer property developer of Malaysia, Berjaya Land Berhad thus bears the promise of quality interior as well as outer finishing.

From this place, travelling to any part of the city will not be an issue as some major KTM stations such as Bandar Tasik Selatan, Serdang, Pantai Dalam, Petaling are present within 3 km of radius. For giving proper education to your children, there are numerous education institutes such as Smk Bukit Jalil, Institut Sukan Negara, Tpm Academy and Asia Pacific University of Technology and Innovation. Getting immediate medical attention is also very easy due to the presence of followings; Klinik Mediviron, Klinik Elamedic, Dentiste’Clinic and Yan Specialist Women Clinic. You can also fetch groceries for youe daily needs from major shopping destinations such as 7-Eleven, Carrefour, Endah Parade and KK Supermart etc.

Arena Green is marking its presence near Bukit Jalil therefore; it is hardly a case that you will feel bored as there are plenty of attractive places nearby to roam around. Th Parliament house is present few kilometres away and also is the Roller Sports World to have a good time with your mate. Those who are art lovers they can make their presence at Islamic Arts Museum present near to Jalan Lembah. Now, if you love to get massage do hit places like Reborn Foot Reflexology and Ozmosis Health & Day spa.

Most of the condos in Bukit Jalil have parking issues but same is not the case over here as you will get a wide covered parking area where your costly sport car can even glide in very easily. To recreate some unforgettable moments with the dearer ones, there is a club house present exclusively for the insiders of Arena Green and also, a Mini Market is situated downstairs to take care of the daily needs of the residents. The list of additional amenities includes the elements like a saloon, a cafeteria and a 24-hour convenient store; this is quite impossible to get at any other nearby condo under such budget price range. Fitness freaks can best utilise their time by running around a Jogging Track or by playing some activities inside a wide Playground present backside.

Double Storey Terrace House.
24’ X 70’
4 Bedrooms & 3 Bathrooms
5 units air conditioners

Rental is RM2k per month

Jalan Putra Bistari 2/1J, Putra Heights, stands out due to its strategic location, excellent connectivity, abundant amenities, and future growth potential, making it a smart choice for Tenants, homeowners and investors seeking convenience and value.

1. Strategic Location

Prime Connectivity
- Close to major highways like LDP, KESAS, ELITE, and SKVE, ensuring smooth access to Kuala Lumpur, Putrajaya, Cyberjaya, and Klang.
- Proximity to Putra Heights MRT & LRT Station (within a short drive), offering seamless public transport to key areas like KLCC, Puchong, and Subang Jaya.

Near Established Neighborhoods
- Adjacent to Subang Jaya, Puchong, and USJ, providing easy access to shopping malls, schools, and business hubs.

2. Excellent Accessibility

🚗 Easy Commute
Direct link to Putrajaya-Cyberjaya Expressway for fast travel to government offices and tech hubs.
-KLIA & KLIA2 within ~30-40 minutes via ELITE Highway.

🚆 Public Transport Friendly
- Putra Heights Integrated Transport Hub (MRT & LRT) nearby, making it ideal for daily commuters.

3. Abundant Amenities Nearby
🛍️ Shopping & Dining:
- AEON BiG Putra Heights (within 5-10 mins)
- Empire Subang & Sunway Pyramid (~15-20 mins drive)
- Various cafes, restaurants, and local eateries in the vicinity.

🏥 Healthcare Facilities:
- Columbia Asia Hospital (Puchong)
- Sunway Medical Centre (Subang Jaya)

🎓 Education Institutions:
- Putra Heights International School
- SJK(C) Chee Wen (Puchong)
- Universiti Putra Malaysia (UPM) & Taylor’s University (nearby)

4. Family-Friendly & Safe Neighborhood

🏡 Quiet & Well-Planned Community:
- Low-density residential area with less traffic congestion compared to busy urban zones.
- Gated & guarded options available for enhanced security.

🌳 Recreational Spaces:
- Putra Heights Park & Playgrounds for outdoor activities.
- Putra Heights Golf Club nearby for golf enthusiasts.

5. Future Growth Potential

📈 Rapid Development in Putra Heights:
- New commercial projects & infrastructure upgrades increasing property value.
- Proximity to Cyberjaya & KLIA Aeropolis boosts long-term investment appeal.

6. Affordable & High-Quality Living

💰 Competitive Property Rental Prices:
- More affordable compared to central Subang Jaya or KL, yet offers modern conveniences.
- Ideal for young professionals, families, and executives looking for a balanced lifestyle
